{
  "stem": "597.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The-- But then the people from Russia, they put up-- the head of the-- of the town was like the-- the-- was a Russian guy.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He-- He installed the rules from Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And just the working people to do something with it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the more the businesspeople was not too  good for the businesspeople.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They started to-- They didn't give you good work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You couldn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Part of because your-- your father was a businessman, the put up in the passport that your father's a businessman, it's not good.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "If they put  it up as a little businessman, it was a little bit better.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But if he is a big businessman, they wouldn't let you out from the city.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But fortunately, my father was written.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He is a good man, so they put it up little businessman.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I had opportunity to go to a different city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Get schooling, get education, more education, like the Rowne, the biggest city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then, therefore, 19-- the end of 19-- 1940-- '39, I went to another, like in January, went to another school there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was getting-- They pay me for schooling.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "In Russia, they pay for schooling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They give you board, room and board, and they pay extra-- extra roubles in packet, and you should go to school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I was in school there from January '39, '40, till the war, '41, I was in school there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The big town.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Was a big experience for me, because I never went out from my town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I met some different girls from different towns.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And boys, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And used to have-- but we had-- you had to-- you have to learn very hard.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It's very hard, because we had new languages.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
